<div class="content row">
  <%= link_to 'Back', emergency_transfers_path %>
</div>

<div class="content row">
  <table class="table table-bordered">
      <tr class="summary-header"><td colspan="4"><b>Emergency Transfer Summary (Form 34L-D)</b></td></tr>

      <tr><td colspan="4"><b>Transferring Facility</b></td></tr>
      <tr>
        <td colspan="1">Name<br /><br />
          <span style="color: #0000ff"><%= @facility&.name %></span>
        </td>
        <td colspan="3">&nbsp;</td>
      </tr>

      <tr>
        <td colspan="4"><b>Patient Information</b></td>
      </tr>

      <tr>
        <td>First Name<br /><br />
          <span style="color: #0000ff"><%= @patient.first_name %></span>
        </td>

        <td>Middle Name<br /><br />
          <span style="color: #0000ff"><%= @patient.middle_name %></span>
        </td>

        <td>Last Name<br /><br />
          <span style="color: #0000ff"><%= @patient.last_name %></span>
        </td>

        <td>Medical Record (MR)<br /><br />
          <span style="color: #0000ff"><%= @patient.mr %></span>
        </td>
      </tr>

      <tr>
        <td colspan="4"><b>Summary</b>
          <br />
          <br />
          This <span style="color: #0000ff"><%= @patient.age %></span>
          years old <span style="color: #0000ff"><%= @patient.gender.sex %></span>
          was admitted to <span style="color: #0000ff"><%= @facility.name %></span>
          on <span style="color: #0000ff"><%= @patient.admission.moment.strftime('%Y-%m-%d') %></span>
          at <span style="color: #0000ff"><%= @patient.admission.moment.strftime('%H:%M') %></span>
          due to <span style="color: #0000ff"><%= admission_diagnoses(@patient)%></span>.

          The observed symptoms on admission were
          <span style="color: #0000ff"><%= admission_symptoms(@patient)%></span>.

          <span style="color: #0000ff"><%= admission_observations(@patient)%></span>.

          Upon asking about known allergies, the patient disclosed
          <span style="color: #0000ff"><%= allergies(@patient)%></span>.

          Upon asking about chronic conditions, the patient disclosed
          <span style="color: #0000ff"><%= chronic_conditions(@patient)%></span>.

          The patient was administered with
          <span style="color: #0000ff"><%= medications(@patient)%></span>.

          The staff performed
          <span style="color: #0000ff"><%= diagnostic_procedures(@patient)%></span>.

          Our team proceeded to
          <span style="color: #0000ff"><%= treatments(@patient) %></span>.
          </span>
        </td>
      </tr>
  </table>
</div>
